description.en: The MonopolyMeta is a virtual reality (VR) game. Players explore a 3D virtual world and purchase digital with the native ERC-20 token from MonopolyMeta, MANA, and digital LAND, which they own permanently. They can buy other goods and services on the MonopolyMeta marketplace.
